sentences: Kim Ji-yeon (Korean: 김지연; born August 19, 1995), better known by her stage name Bona, is a South Korean singer and actress.
She made her acting debut in the KBS2 drama Hit the Top (2017), and was cast as the female lead in the teen drama Girls' Generation 1979 (2018).
